name: Nokia 3310 Warm Red
description: To satiate the nostalgia or for someone who wishes to go for a so-called “smartphone detox”, there are cheaper options like Nokia 150, Nokia 130, Nokia 216 and others. However, if you wish to go for the Nokia 3310 for reasons best known to you, here is a glimpse of what you get. Colour options include Warm Red (Glossy), Dark Blue (Matte), Yellow (Glossy) and Grey (MatteFor a price of Rs 3,310, the Nokia 3310 offers a 2.4-inch TFT colour display with a resolution of 240 X 320 pixels. It is a dual SIM 2.5G GSM handset powered by S30+ operating system and a 1,200mAh battery. The handset supports 32GB of external storage.
